## Next Steps for Deployment

To start collecting analytics data:

1. **Enable in Vercel Dashboard**:
   - Go to your project settings in Vercel
   - Navigate to the Analytics section
   - Enable Web Analytics for your project

2. **Deploy**:
   - Deploy your project to Vercel: `vercel deploy`
   - Analytics will automatically start tracking once deployed

3. **Verify**:
   - Visit your deployed site
   - Check browser Network tab for requests to `/_vercel/insights/view`
   - View analytics data in your Vercel dashboard

## Notes
- The Analytics component is lightweight and will not impact page load performance
- Data collection is GDPR compliant and privacy-focused
- No changes were needed as the configuration is already complete and correct
